venue.address_1: Old Troy Rd & Old Marlborough Rd
venue.name: Mt Monadnock - Dublin Trail

item.description:
I want to get one more practice hike on Monadnock in before I head to Peru for a couple of treks in June. Monadnock can't match the oxygen depleted altitude of the Andes but heck, a little tune up on the legs can't hurt? I know it's been done a few times this year but just putting it out there if anyone feels like joining me. I'll be starting early, 8:30am as I have a busy afternoon...

UPDATE 8:30pm 05/25 - I just had to cancel myself...  My afternoon plans were moved up and I don't have enough time to get out there, hike and get back... I left this open as Earl and Tom are going...  Sorry about that!

group.name: Northern Central MA, Southern NH Hiking Group

item.name: Last Minute... Monadnock via Dublin this Saturday?
